comment:
* Base column for the table that contain Carrier Public key.
     * @hide

variables.name: KEY_TYPE
variables.comment:
* KeyType whether the key is being used for WLAN or ePDG. *

Type: INTEGER

variables.name: PUBLIC_KEY
variables.comment:
* The carrier public key that is used for the IMSI encryption. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: KEY_IDENTIFIER
variables.comment:
* The key identifier Attribute value pair that helps a server locate * the private key to decrypt the permanent identity. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: EXPIRATION_TIME
variables.comment:
* Date-Time in UTC when the key will expire. *

Type: INTEGER (long)

variables.name: LAST_MODIFIED
variables.comment:
* Timestamp when this table was last modified, in milliseconds since * January 1, 1970 00:00:00.0 UTC. *

Type: INTEGER (long)

variables.name: CARRIER_ID
variables.comment:
* Carrier ID of the operetor. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: CONTENT_URI
variables.comment: * The {@code content://} style URL for this table.
